{"settings":"{
	"window.zoomLevel": 0,

	"editor.fontWeight": 400,
	"cSpell.ignoreWords": ["prathamesh"],

	Most fav fonts:
	1. Operator mono
	2. Dank Mono
	3. Fira code
	4. Jetbrains Mono
	5. "Rec Mono Duotone"
	6. IBM PLex Mono

		Fira code, Operator mono, Cascadia code, Dank Mono,Victor Mono,Bahnschrift,Inconsolata,Fira code iScript, Fantasque Sans Mono, Jetbrains Mono,Hack,Monoid,Bitstream Vera Sans Mono,IBM PLex Mono, Rec Mono Duotone, Rec Mono Linear"
	*/
	"workbench.statusBar.visible": true,
	"cSpell.enabledLanguageIds": [
		"asciidoc",
		"c",
		"cpp",
		"csharp",
		"css",
		"git-commit",
		"go",
		"handlebars",

		"typescriptreact",
		"yaml",
		"yml"

	"editor.lineHeight": 20,
	"editor.suggestSelection": "first",
	"vsintellicode.modify.editor.suggestSelection": "automaticallyOverrodeDefaultValue",
	"python.jediEnabled": false,
	"[javascript]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
		"editor.rulers": [80]
	},
	"[handlebar]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
		"editor.rulers": [80]
	},
	"java.home": "C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk-8",
	"java.help.firstView": "gettingStarted",
	"liveServer.settings.donotVerifyTags": true,
	"sync.gist": "53fbda27227767ac6a18245beb0c94a2",
	"[html]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	"[javascriptreact]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	"[json]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},

	"editor.renderLineHighlight": "none", //Very very important
	"editor.rulers": [80], // Regular
	"[python]": {
		"editor.rulers": [80],
		"editor.insertSpaces": false,
		"editor.tabSize": 4,
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	//"editor.wordWrapColumn": 0,
	"editor.formatOnPaste": true,
	"editor.formatOnSave": true,
	"editor.formatOnType": true,
	"editor.wordWrap": "bounded",
	"chaliceIcons.showArrows": true,
	"workbench.activityBar.visible": true,

	"breadcrumbs.enabled": true,

		"git-commit": true,
		"plaintext": true,
		"json": true,
		"javascript": true,
		"python": true,
		"html": true,
		"javascriptreact": true
	},
	"editor.tokenColorCustomizations": {
		"textMateRules": [
			{
				"name": "One Dark italic",
				"scope": [
					"comment",
					"entity.other.attribute-name",
					"keyword",
					"markup.underline.link",
					"storage.modifier",
					"storage.type",
					"string.url",
					"variable.language.super",
					"variable.language.this"
				],
				"settings": {
					"fontStyle": "italic"
				}
			},
			{
				"name": "One Dark italic reset",
				"scope": [
					"keyword.operator",
					"keyword.other.type",
					"storage.modifier.import",
					"storage.modifier.package",
					"storage.type.built-in",
					"storage.type.function.arrow",
					"storage.type.generic",
					"storage.type.java",
					"storage.type.primitive"
				],
				"settings": {
					"fontStyle": ""
				}
			}
		]

	"liveshare.presence": false,
	"editor.renameOnType": true,
	"wrapSelection.patterns": {},

	},
	"emmet.includeLanguages": {
		"javascript": "javascriptreact"
	},
	"javascript.updateImportsOnFileMove.enabled": "always",
	"[markdown]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	"editor.cursorBlinking": "expand",
	"python.autoComplete.addBrackets": true,
	"python.languageServer": "Pylance",
	"workbench.startupEditor": "welcomePage",
	"diffEditor.ignoreTrimWhitespace": false,
	"python.languageServer": "Microsoft",
	"workbench.iconTheme": "mosmmy-icons-vscode",
	"[dart]": {
		"editor.formatOnSave": true,
		"editor.formatOnType": true,
		"editor.rulers": [80],
		"editor.selectionHighlight": false,
		"editor.suggest.snippetsPreventQuickSuggestions": false,
		"editor.suggestSelection": "first",
		"editor.tabCompletion": "onlySnippets",
		"editor.wordBasedSuggestions": false
	},
	"editor.renderWhitespace": "boundary",
	"workbench.colorTheme": "Moonlight II Italic",
	"editor.fontSize": 15
